com.dhemery.victor.frank

Interface Frank

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FranklyFrank, PublishingFrank

    public interface Frank
    An agent that can communicate with a Frank server.

    • Method Detail

      • accessibilityCheck

        boolean accessibilityCheck()
        Report whether accessibility is enabled in the device. Note that Frank automatically enables accessibility, so this method is obsolete.

      • appExec

        String appExec(String name,
             Object... arguments)
        Send a message to the application delegate.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the message.
        arguments - the message arguments.
        Returns:
        the application delegate's response to the message.

      • dump

        String dump()
        Retrieve a JSON description of the tree of views in the application's main window.

      • map

        List<String> map(String engine,
               String query,
               String name,
               Object... arguments)
        Send a message to a set of views.
        Parameters:
        engine - the name of the selector engine to select recipients for the message
        query - the pattern for the selector engine to use to select recipients
        name - the name of the message
        arguments - the message arguments
        Returns:
        the list of responses, one from each recipient

        Report the application's orientation.
